complaint.body:
Hello,

I received my order today but the product was completely damaged. The packaging was crushed and the item inside is broken.

Order details:
- Order ID: #{order_id}
- Item: {product_name}
- Date ordered: {order_date}

I have attached photos of the damage. This is very disappointing as this was a gift for my {occasion}. Please advise on how to proceed with a replacement or refund.

Sincerely,
{sender_name}

I am writing to report a billing error on my account.

I was charged ${wrong_amount} on {charge_date} for my monthly subscription, but my plan is only ${correct_amount}/month.

Account email: {account_email}
Account ID: ACC-{account_id}

This is the third time this has happened. I need this corrected immediately and a refund issued for the overcharge. If this continues, I will cancel my subscription.

Frustrated,
{sender_name}

order.body:
Hi,

Please find attached our purchase order for 50 enterprise licenses (PO #{po_number}).

Items:
- Enterprise License x50: ${price_per} each
- Total: ${total_price}
- Delivery: Digital download

Billing address: {company_name}, {address}

Please confirm receipt and provide invoice.

Thank you,
{sender_name}
Procurement Manager, {company}

Hello,

I placed order #{order_id} yesterday and realized I need to make a change before it ships.

Current order: {current_item} x{current_qty}
Requested change: {new_item} x{new_qty}

Is it possible to modify this before it goes out? Please let me know as soon as possible as I assume it may ship soon.

Thanks,
{sender_name}

support.body:
Hello,

Your software crashed while I was working on an important project. When I restarted it, some of my work appears to be missing.

Details:
- Software version: {version}
- OS: {os_name}
- Last autosave: {last_save}
- Missing data: approximately {missing_amount} of work

I have the crash log attached. This is critical as I have a client deadline tomorrow.

Please help recover my data as soon as possible.

{sender_name}
